summary: Save level one inside Helgen keep. I made her a little softer in appearance than your typical Orc. She isn't as tanky. She has the Helgen keep key and an iron sword.
descriptionHtml:
Save level one inside Helgen keep. I made her a little softer in appearance than your typical Orc. She isn't as tanky. She has the Helgen keep key and an iron sword. She is my first attempt at a somewhat attractive Orc and only my third upload on the Nexus.
